   "widgets_values": [
    "RAW -> ACEScg (the honest chain)\n\nAtlasLoadRAW demosaics ONCE and writes a scene-linear EXR sidecar tagged\n'Linear Rec.709 (sRGB)' \u2014 rawpy's true primaries, deliberately never\nmislabelled ACEScg.\n\n\ud83d\udce4 AtlasExportPlateEXR then converts that FILE float-to-float through\nOCIO into a real ACEScg EXR (oiio:ColorSpace tagged). It never passes\nthrough Comfy's 8-bit display-referred IMAGE tensor \u2014 which is exactly\nwhy saving EXRs from normal image nodes can't produce a usable ACEScg\nplate. The converted ref feeds AtlasAttachSourcePlate, so every DCC\nexport references the ACEScg plate.\n\nhalf_size ON for fast iteration on the 36MP NEF; OFF for final quality."
   ],
   "title": "README \u00b7 ACEScg",
   "color": "#432",
   "bgcolor": "#653",
   "id": 3,
   "flags": {},
